{"id":549,"ayahs":[{"number":1,"arabic":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ لَا تَتَّخِذُوا۟ عَدُوِّى وَعَدُوَّكُمْ أَوْلِيَآءَ تُلْقُونَ إِلَيْهِم بِٱلْمَوَدَّةِ وَقَدْ كَفَرُوا۟ بِمَا جَآءَكُم مِّنَ ٱلْحَقِّ يُخْرِجُونَ ٱلرَّسُولَ وَإِيَّاكُمْ ۙ أَن تُؤْمِنُوا۟ بِٱللَّهِ رَبِّكُمْ إِن كُنتُمْ خَرَجْتُمْ جِهَٰدًۭا فِى سَبِيلِى وَٱبْتِغَآءَ مَرْضَاتِى ۚ تُسِرُّونَ إِلَيْهِم بِٱلْمَوَدَّةِ وَأَنَا۠ أَعْلَمُ بِمَآ أَخْفَيْتُمْ وَمَآ أَعْلَنتُمْ ۚ وَمَن يَفْعَلْهُ مِنكُمْ فَقَدْ ضَلَّ سَوَآءَ ٱلسَّبِيلِ","translation":"O YOU who have attained to faith! Do not take My enemies - who are your enemies as well - for your friends, showing them affection even though they are bent on denying whatever truth has come unto you, [and even though] they have driven the Apostle and yourselves away, [only] because you believe in God, your Sustainer! If [it be true that] you have gone forth [from your homes] to strive in My cause, and out of a longing for My goodly acceptance, [do not take them for your friends,] inclining towards them in secret affection: for I am fully aware of all that you may conceal as well as of all that you do openly. And any of you who does this has already strayed from the right path.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5151.mp3","surahId":60,"words":[{"id":391,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"ওহে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":392,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":393,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছ","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":394,"position":4,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":395,"position":5,"arabic":"تَتَّخِذُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা গ্রহণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":396,"position":6,"arabic":"عَدُوِّى","translation":"আমার শত্রুকে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":397,"position":7,"arabic":"وَعَدُوَّكُمْ","translation":"ও তোমাদের শত্রুকে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":398,"position":8,"arabic":"أَوْلِيَآءَ","translation":"বন্ধুরূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":399,"position":9,"arabic":"تُلْقُونَ","translation":"তোমরা স্থাপন কর","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":400,"position":10,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِم","translation":"তাদের সাথেে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":401,"position":11,"arabic":"بِٱلْمَوَدَّةِ","translation":"বন্ধুত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":402,"position":12,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"অথচ নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":403,"position":13,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"ত্রা অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":404,"position":14,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":405,"position":15,"arabic":"جَآءَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের কাছে এসেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":406,"position":16,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":407,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْحَقِّ","translation":"সত্য","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":408,"position":18,"arabic":"يُخْرِجُونَ","translation":"তারা বহিষ্কার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":409,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسُولَ","translation":"রসূলকে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":410,"position":20,"arabic":"وَإِيَّاكُمْ ۙ","translation":"এবং তোমাদেরকেও","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":412,"position":21,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"একারণে যে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":413,"position":22,"arabic":"تُؤْمِنُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":414,"position":23,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":415,"position":24,"arabic":"رَبِّكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের রব","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":416,"position":25,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":417,"position":26,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":418,"position":27,"arabic":"خَرَجْتُمْ","translation":"বের হয়ে থাকো","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":419,"position":28,"arabic":"جِهَـٰدًۭا","translation":"জিহাদে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":420,"position":29,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"(মধ্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":421,"position":30,"arabic":"سَبِيلِى","translation":"আমার পথে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":422,"position":31,"arabic":"وَٱبْتِغَآءَ","translation":"ও সন্ধানে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":423,"position":32,"arabic":"مَرْضَاتِى ۚ","translation":"আমার সন্তুষ্টির","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":425,"position":33,"arabic":"تُسِرُّونَ","translation":"তোমরা গোপনে কর","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":426,"position":34,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِم","translation":"তাদের সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":427,"position":35,"arabic":"بِٱلْمَوَدَّةِ","translation":"বন্ধুত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":428,"position":36,"arabic":"وَأَنَا۠","translation":"আমি অথচ","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":429,"position":37,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","translation":"সম্যক অবগত","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":430,"position":38,"arabic":"بِمَآ","translation":"যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":431,"position":39,"arabic":"أَخْفَيْتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা গোপন কর","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":432,"position":40,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"ও যা","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_042.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":433,"position":41,"arabic":"أَعْلَنتُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমরা প্রকাশ কর","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_043.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":435,"position":42,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_045.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":436,"position":43,"arabic":"يَفْعَلْهُ","translation":"তা করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_046.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":437,"position":44,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_047.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":438,"position":45,"arabic":"فَقَدْ","translation":"অতঃপর নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_048.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":439,"position":46,"arabic":"ضَلَّ","translation":"ভ্রষ্ট হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_049.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":440,"position":47,"arabic":"سَوَآءَ","translation":"সোজা","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_050.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":441,"position":48,"arabic":"ٱلسَّبِيلِ","translation":"পথ থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_001_051.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":442,"position":49,"arabic":"١","translation":"(১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":2,"arabic":"إِن يَثْقَفُوكُمْ يَكُونُوا۟ لَكُمْ أَعْدَآءًۭ وَيَبْسُطُوٓا۟ إِلَيْكُمْ أَيْدِيَهُمْ وَأَلْسِنَتَهُم بِٱلسُّوٓءِ وَوَدُّوا۟ لَوْ تَكْفُرُونَ","translation":"If they could but overcome you, they would [still] remain your foes, and would stretch forth their hands and tongues against you with evil intent: for they desire that you [too] should deny the truth.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5152.mp3","surahId":60,"words":[{"id":1316,"position":1,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1317,"position":2,"arabic":"يَثْقَفُوكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের কাবু করতে পারে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1318,"position":3,"arabic":"يَكُونُوا۟","translation":"তারা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1319,"position":4,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1320,"position":5,"arabic":"أَعْدَآءًۭ","translation":"শত্রু","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1321,"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَبْسُطُوٓا۟","translation":"ও তারা সম্প্রসারিত করে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1322,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَيْكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের দিবে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1323,"position":8,"arabic":"أَيْدِيَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের হাতগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1324,"position":9,"arabic":"وَأَلْسِنَتَهُم","translation":"ও তাদের রসনাগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1325,"position":10,"arabic":"بِٱلسُّوٓءِ","translation":"মন্দের সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1326,"position":11,"arabic":"وَوَدُّوا۟","translation":"ও তারা কামনা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1327,"position":12,"arabic":"لَوْ","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1328,"position":13,"arabic":"تَكْفُرُونَ","translation":"তোমরা কাফির হও","audioUrl":"wbw/060_002_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":1329,"position":14,"arabic":"٢","translation":"(২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":3,"arabic":"لَن تَنفَعَكُمْ أَرْحَامُكُمْ وَلَآ أَوْلَٰدُكُمْ ۚ يَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ يَفْصِلُ بَيْنَكُمْ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ بِمَا تَعْمَلُونَ بَصِيرٌۭ","translation":"But [bear in mind that] neither your kinsfolk nor [even] your own children will be of any benefit to you on Resurrection Day, [for then] He will decide between you [on your merit alone]: and God sees all that you do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5153.mp3","surahId":60,"words":[{"id":2382,"position":1,"arabic":"لَن","translation":"কখনো না","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2383,"position":2,"arabic":"تَنفَعَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের উপকার দেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2384,"position":3,"arabic":"أَرْحَامُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের আত্মীয়দের","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2385,"position":4,"arabic":"وَلَآ","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2386,"position":5,"arabic":"أَوْلَـٰدُكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের সন্তানদের","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2388,"position":6,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","translation":"দিনে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2389,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ","translation":"কিয়ামতের","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2390,"position":8,"arabic":"يَفْصِلُ","translation":"বিচ্ছেদ করবেন তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2391,"position":9,"arabic":"بَيْنَكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2393,"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2394,"position":11,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2395,"position":12,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা কাজ কর","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2396,"position":13,"arabic":"بَصِيرٌۭ","translation":"সব দেখেন","audioUrl":"wbw/060_003_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":2397,"position":14,"arabic":"٣","translation":"(৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":4,"arabic":"قَدْ كَانَتْ لَكُمْ أُسْوَةٌ حَسَنَةٌۭ فِىٓ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ وَٱلَّذِينَ مَعَهُۥٓ إِذْ قَالُوا۟ لِقَوْمِهِمْ إِنَّا بُرَءَٰٓؤُا۟ مِنكُمْ وَمِمَّا تَعْبُدُونَ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ كَفَرْنَا بِكُمْ وَبَدَا بَيْنَنَا وَبَيْنَكُمُ ٱلْعَدَٰوَةُ وَٱلْبَغْضَآءُ أَبَدًا حَتَّىٰ تُؤْمِنُوا۟ بِٱللَّهِ وَحْدَهُۥٓ إِلَّا قَوْلَ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ لِأَبِيهِ لَأَسْتَغْفِرَنَّ لَكَ وَمَآ أَمْلِكُ لَكَ مِنَ ٱللَّهِ مِن شَىْءٍۢ ۖ رَّبَّنَا عَلَيْكَ تَوَكَّلْنَا وَإِلَيْكَ أَنَبْنَا وَإِلَيْكَ ٱلْمَصِيرُ","translation":"Indeed, you have had a good example in Abraham and those who followed him, when they said unto their [idolatrous] people: \"Verily, we are quit of you and of all that you worship instead of God: we deny the truth of whatever you believe; and between us and you there has arisen enmity and hatred, to last until such a time as you come to believe in the One God!\" The only exception was Abraham's saying to his father \"I shall indeed pray for [God's] forgiveness for thee, although I have it not in my power to obtain anything from God in thy behalf.\" [And Abraham and his followers prayed:] \"O our Sustainer! In Thee have we placed our trust, and unto Thee do we turn: for unto Thee is all journeys' end.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5154.mp3","surahId":60,"words":[{"id":3739,"position":1,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চই","audioUrl":"wbw/060_004_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3740,"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَتْ","translation":"রয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/060_004_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3741,"position":3,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/060_004_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3742,"position":4,"arabic":"أُسْوَةٌ","translation":"আদর্শ","audioUrl":"wbw/060_004_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":3743,"position":5,"arabic":"حَسَنَةٌۭ","translation":"উত্তম","audioUr